    • Constructor Detail

      • User

        public User(java.lang.String name,
            java.lang.String password)
        Create a user with a given username and password. Privacy level will be set to 1 by default and privilege will be set to user
        Parameters:
        name - username string. Should be lower case and unique
        password - password string. Should be hashed with sha-256 and encoded with UTF-8

      • User

        public User()
        Creates a user with default privacy 1 and default privilege USER. Name and password will be null

        Attempts to add a user to the User list friends
        Parameters:
        user - The user to add to friends
        Returns:
        True if the user was added. False if (1. the user is already in list (can't add the same person twice) or 2. the user has the same id as the parents of the friend list (can't add yourself))
